{"tid":1464412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住團結永遠係我哋最強嘅武器","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:12.000Z","uid":2762,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd8605b0698cbec2f7c3389ef54666feaba5838","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"由今日阻旅客到圍公安一事，見到好多人都有分歧。<br />\n但記住我哋一開始嘅信念：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割蓆</span><br />\n<br />\n依家連登有好多借機起哄嘅留言，大部分都係P牌仔<br />\n我相信佢哋潛伏咗喺度好耐，<br />\n但記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋不斷嘈交，佢哋就愈開心</span><br />\n正如隔離Po講，鬼其實不嬲都有，而且捉唔晒<br />\n而我哋可以做嘅只可以唔好受佢哋分化。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做得唔好可以檢討，有麻煩一齊拆，唔掂講到掂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但一散就咩都冇</span><br />\n所以前線做咩都好，現場同外界總有落差，<br />\n但記住永不分割！各有各做，唔認同嘅先傾下，唔好受人屌兩聲就起哄，如果唔係就變成不斷鬧<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結，不分割，一齊頂住</span>"},{"pid":"fb7c22a26f03f314b12f1a59f6bbfd39fb65d921","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148490463c45e47a0cc2a10d85025bdfddbac19b","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61228268ad014353700c2dd2afc064dfcd5163bb","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a85c62cb1a3e4b5be5509b40151f3600234810d","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f45a753f1b89aae4315fbbd0e56566e13fb39213","tid":1464412,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"0ebac4199faebf4a60e8ad4cf947b9f8c338a478","tid":1464412,"uid":17334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"大家兄弟有咩唔掂講到掂"},{"pid":"3fe376a12647d0047c4d55a03afd23deeec52961","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd0876d15c11fc38a93a85a76cea6b5dde0768a8","tid":1464412,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n入機場手足可以睇睇，如果覺得講得啱，唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"19672bec158dc4ff5843fc6f7e995e9656300c3b","tid":1464412,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家冷靜<br />\n小心有狗/公安想打死人<br />\n苦肉計</span>"},{"pid":"c50db4cb1e76bb4272ebd9a67bcba10ba1853889","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ebac4199faebf4a60e8ad4cf947b9f8c338a478","tid":1464412,"uid":17334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"大家兄弟有咩唔掂講到掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"係 大家想要嘅嘢一樣，做法唔同可以傾，可以檢討，但一散就冇"},{"pid":"5dc044aca52082c7854a4a4ba601eb384f6c1411","tid":1464412,"uid":134321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dcb2dfca276a4efb38c260c6caec743d465e6b1","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"記住不割蓆"},{"pid":"5429dcd6c53c42cb4792dfcbeb24a0d7de5e20d6","tid":1464412,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"成堆話捉住公安無意思<br />\n有堆平時唔講野 而家叫人針對翻五大訴求<br />\n仲有咩2支木代表唔到咩<br />\n<br />\n屌你啦 拎支鐳射筆都瓜瓜嘈<br />\n2支木棍叫無咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀 唔好唔記得內地公職人員係唔可以跨境執法<br />\n拎埋電話分分睇到斷正告得上國際法庭同俾英國出師有名<br />\n<br />\n 呢2個鐘成班五毛黑警俾人周到勁緊張收order上黎洗版"},{"pid":"abf60bfcad6a996d73c21bfb6345ea394c45fb2b","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"有人不斷話要打嘅 先勸下佢同佢傾<br />\n唔好一開始就鬧咗先"},{"pid":"ab9aa5ad5ea8f1f878cdbfc9e2c7021d9e039765","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15949613c22cd3f231e39175ca4a8b39dbc334d8","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cdf5e550ed161d935bbeb2a1faddb440d7d60c6","tid":1464412,"uid":49508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽 = 分化<br />\n冷氣軍師 = 收聲<br />\n塊蓆就黎得返堆粉<br />\n大家繼續嘈落去 中共又做最大贏家喇"},{"pid":"700678dd4f339a9597dc2c968379a4822a2fc1d3","tid":1464412,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"唔好畀呢個信息沉"},{"pid":"c51683cde570bc4d8288df001cef4b16e1841c1c","tid":1464412,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!!  NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJqUoKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJqUoKL.jpg&h=77a18472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugkASC5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugkASC5.png&h=0378ec51&s={SIZE}\" />